articles.author: Jacopo Barigazzi
articles.title: Ukraine claps back after Russia puts Zelenskyy on 'wanted list' - POLITICO Europe
articles.description: Moscow has sought to kill the Ukrainian president since the beginning of its full-scale invasion.
articles.content: The addition of Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy to the Kremlin’s “wanted list” shows “the desperation of the Russian state machine and propaganda,” Ukraine’s ministry of foreign affairs wrote… [+989 chars]
